Everyday AT Money Challenge ENHANCED
Master money skills with graduated hints, undo, visual feedback, and progress analytics.

Welcome!

Hi everyone!

This activity is designed to help you build real-world money skills that you can use every day at work, in the community, or while shopping with friends. Go at your own pace, have fun, and be proud of your progress. Each time you practice, you're growing your independence, confidence, and readiness for life beyond school. Keep it up, you're doing great!
Mr. K - ATP Teacher

Four Practice Modes:

  • Practice Mode: Count bills and coins with visual highlighting
  • Next Dollar Up: Learn to pay using the next whole dollar strategy
  • Shop Mode: Drag money to pay exact amounts
  • Cashier Mode: Make correct change for customers
